{"tid":970861,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[求意見]另一半生日應該點慶祝好","createTime":"2019-01-06T07:48:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-06T13:03:54.000Z","uid":59165,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"07dd6be4aff8c87c85823c0f2a7adada36e554f5","tid":970861,"uid":59165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T07:48:38.000Z","msg":"佢生日撞正星期六日<br />\n<br />\nplan a係星期六去aia玩+雜技表演 $130門票+$300代幣套票(1人有20個代幣玩)+$400-500睇雜技表演<br />\n<br />\n但係無預星期六dinner<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n夜晚可以返屋企訓 因為佢會掛住屋企隻寵物<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n星期日夜晚另外book左餐廳食<br />\n<br />\nplan b係星期六澳門酒店套票$1450 包一餐dinner buffet 一晚酒店 2船飛<br />\n可能會另外加錢睇個咩蝙蝠俠展覽<br />\n<br />\n但係去到個邊晏就又會飲飲食食 (之前話有幾間想lunch去食)<br />\n夜晚係酒店又好似on99唔知做咩好<br />\n第日又無野做食完lunch就走<br />\n一樣星期日夜晚另外book左餐廳食<br />\n<br />\n大家覺得邊樣抵d？<br />\n因為佢有做星期日教興趣班 佢都傾向想星期日有得教學生 <br />\n但係aia個plan相比起去澳門又好似唔係好抵咁<br />\n<br />\n好糾結<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n或者會唔會有其他意見 感謝"},{"pid":"f4e99a152b86a7f084eb0c9d0b3979fac850bc7a","tid":970861,"uid":223593,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T07:57:17.000Z","msg":"Plan B好好多<br />\n去aia玩買代幣都買幾舊"},{"pid":"1c31d2bbfe2b8f941f7683aac8b29f52c9b49cef","tid":970861,"uid":108236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T08:08:44.000Z","msg":"屌住過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a6fa4696cb420902119b5fb25dc88ed1e23caeb","tid":970861,"uid":11698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T08:16:26.000Z","msg":"去酒店扑野啦"},{"pid":"53ddbbe1342aff78bf647f753e4814d7cd535209","tid":970861,"uid":56197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T08:24:10.000Z","msg":"夜晚係酒店大戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/diu.gif\" class=